        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="BIOS设置"><a href="#BIOS设置" class="headerlink" title="BIOS设置"></a>BIOS设置</h3><p>联想E470 启动BIOS为开机后Enter-&gt;F1，如果只是指定磁盘启动顺序则只需要F12。<br>特别的，Win10如果想要修改BIOS相关内容需要，取消设置里的快速启动，并(shif+点击关机)-&gt;疑难解答-&gt;高级选项-&gt;UEFI固件设置。</p><h3 id="虚拟环境安装scrapy"><a href="#虚拟环境安装scrapy" class="headerlink" title="虚拟环境安装scrapy"></a>虚拟环境安装scrapy</h3><ul><li>Ubuntu 18.0.4 LTS使用update-alterantive配置python2/3共存<pre class="line-numbers language-lang-shell"><code class="language-lang-shell"># 添加python版本，并指定优先级sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/local/lib/python3.6 100sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/local/lib/python2.7 200# 选择指定版本sudo update-alternatives --config python<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li><li>创建虚拟环境<pre class="line-numbers language-lang-shell"><code class="language-lang-shell"># 安装virtualenvpip3 install -i https://pypi.douban.com/simple/ virtualenv# 创建虚拟环境目录，与实际代码位置可以不同virtualenv venv_scrapy## 切换虚拟目录cd venv_scrapy && source ./bin/activate## 安装scrapypip3 install -i https://pypi.douban.com/simple/ scrapy## 创建scrapy项目cd ~/Code && scrapy startproject scrapy_prj## 退出虚拟环境deactivate<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li></ul><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content>
      
      
