    <entry>
      <title>单向链表反转</title>
      <link href="/2019/10/06/dan-xiang-lian-biao-fan-zhuan/"/>
      <url>/2019/10/06/dan-xiang-lian-biao-fan-zhuan/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="单向链表反转"><a href="#单向链表反转" class="headerlink" title="单向链表反转"></a>单向链表反转</h1><h2 id="直接递归"><a href="#直接递归" class="headerlink" title="直接递归"></a>直接递归</h2><blockquote><p>时间复杂度$O(n)$，空间复杂度$O(n)$   </p></blockquote><p>简单递归输出就好，适合小数据量。  </p><pre class="line-numbers language-lang-c"><code class="language-lang-c">void reverse(head){    if(head.next == null){        print(head);        return;    }    reverse(head.next);    print(head);}<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="栈存储"><a href="#栈存储" class="headerlink" title="栈存储"></a>栈存储</h2><blockquote><p>时间复杂度$O(n)$，空间复杂度$O(n)$  </p></blockquote><p>分为两种:存储元素地址和存储值，其中地址可以构建出一个新的逆序列表。以存储地址为例：  </p><pre class="line-numbers language-lang-c"><code class="language-lang-c">void reverse(head){    Node cur = head;    while(cur != null){        stack.push(cur);        cur = cur.next;    }    while(!stack.isEmpty){        print(stack.pull());    }}<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="直接遍历"><a href="#直接遍历" class="headerlink" title="直接遍历"></a><del>直接遍历</del></h2><blockquote><p>时间复杂度$O(n^2)$，空间复杂度0</p></blockquote><h2 id="反转链表结构"><a href="#反转链表结构" class="headerlink" title="反转链表结构"></a>反转链表结构</h2><blockquote><p>时间复杂度$O(n)$，空间复杂度0  </p></blockquote><p>这种方法不需要额为的空间，在遍历时调整元素的指向关系。<br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sincatter/picgos/imgs/imgs20191006222506.png" alt="单向链表反转"></p><pre class="line-numbers language-lang-c"><code class="language-lang-c">void reverse(head){    Node* cur = head.next;    Node* pre = head;    pre.next = nullptr;    Node* tmp = nullptr;    while(cur != null){        tmp = cur.next;        cur.next = pre;        pre = cur;        cur = tmp;    }}<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="LeetCode例子"><a href="#LeetCode例子" class="headerlink" title="LeetCode例子"></a>LeetCode例子</h2><h3 id="题目-92-Reverse-Linked-List-II"><a href="#题目-92-Reverse-Linked-List-II" class="headerlink" title="题目 - 92. Reverse Linked List II"></a>题目 - 92. Reverse Linked List II</h3><p>Reverse a linked list from position <em>m</em> to <em>n</em>. Do it in one-pass.<br><strong>Note:</strong> 1 ≤ <em>m</em> ≤ <em>n</em> ≤ length of list.<br><strong>Example:</strong>  </p><blockquote><p><strong>Input:</strong> 1-&gt;2-&gt;3-&gt;4-&gt;5-&gt;NULL, <em>m</em> = 2, <em>n</em> = 4<br><strong>Output:</strong> 1-&gt;4-&gt;3-&gt;2-&gt;5-&gt;NULL</p></blockquote><p>反转从位置 m 到 n 的链表。请使用一趟扫描完成反转。<br><strong>说明:</strong><br>1 ≤ m ≤ n ≤ 链表长度。<br><strong>示例:</strong>  </p><blockquote><p><strong>输入:</strong> 1-&gt;2-&gt;3-&gt;4-&gt;5-&gt;NULL, m = 2, n = 4<br><strong>输出:</strong> 1-&gt;4-&gt;3-&gt;2-&gt;5-&gt;NULL</p></blockquote><h3 id="解答"><a href="#解答" class="headerlink" title="解答"></a>解答</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-lang-c"><code class="language-lang-c">/** * Definition for singly-linked list. * struct ListNode { *     int val; *     ListNode *next; *     ListNode(int x) : val(x), next(NULL) {} * }; */class Solution {public:    ListNode* reverseBetween(ListNode* head, int m, int n) {        ListNode *mNode = new ListNode(0);        ListNode *resNode = nullptr;        ListNode *pre = mNode;        mNode->next = head;        for(int i = 0;i < m - 1; i++){            pre = pre->next;        }        ListNode *cur = pre->next;        ListNode *tmp = nullptr;        for (int i = m; i < n;i++){            tmp = pre->next;            pre->next = cur->next;            cur->next = pre->next->next;            pre->next->next = tmp;        }        resNode = mNode->next;        delete(mNode);        return resNode;    }};<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content>
      
      
